♪A sea of people♪

24
00:01:26,484 --> 00:01:28,036
♪Unafraid of how far it is♪

25
00:01:28,036 --> 00:01:30,724
♪Racing under stars toward you♪

26
00:01:30,724 --> 00:01:31,844
♪But♪

27
00:01:31,844 --> 00:01:32,644
♪Time is heartless♪

28
